headline: U.S. Bancorp (NYSE:USB) Slips 10% Over The Week As Global Trade Tensions Rise
summary: U.S. Bancorp (NYSE:USB) experienced a 10% decline in its stock price over the past week, amid a broader market downturn driven by escalating global trade tensions.
